cloudflare-ip-updater (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Monitors external IP every 3 hours
  * Automatically updates Cloudflare DNS when IP changes
  * Systemd service and timer integration
  * Configuration via /etc/cloudflare-ip-updater/config
  * Auto-detects Zone ID and DNS Record ID if not provided

